Maureen Flannigan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maureen_Flannigan 0 Maureen Osborne Flannigan (born December 30, 1973) is an American actress. She is perhaps best known for her role as teenager Evie Ethel Garland on the fantasy sitcom Out of This World, which ran from 1987 to 1991.
